<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/5.3.0/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/site.css"> 
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/index.css"> 
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - WeatherForecastApp</title>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="video-background">
        <video playsinline autoplay muted loop>
            <source src="https://cdn.pixabay.com/video/2020/04/22/36816-412926058_large.mp4" type="video/mp4">
        </video>
    </div>
    <div class="video-overlay"></div>

    <div class="content-container">
        <div class="info-box">
            <h1 class="display-4">Welcome to Weather Forecast</h1>
            <p>Your reliable source for real-time weather updates and forecasts.</p>
            <p>Developed using ASP.NET Core Web App (MVC Architecture).</p>
            <p>This application provides up-to-date weather information and forecasts for any location worldwide.</p>
            <p>Utilizes the <strong>Weatherbit API</strong> for current weather conditions, detailed forecasts, and historical weather data.</p>
            <p>To get started, use the navigation buttons above.</p>
            <h2>Developed by Muneel Haider</h2>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
